  <brief_title>Assessing Women's Attitudes About the Risk of Infertility Related to Adjuvant Therapy for Early Breast Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Survey of the Breast International Group (B.I.G.) to Assess the Attitude of Patients Aged Less Than 35 Years, With Early Breast Cancer, Toward the Risk of Loss of Fertility Related to Adjuvant Therapies</official_title>
